I love this app. It has proven to be useful on so many occasions. Having a spirit level in your pocket, that is available at the drop of a hat, is a must, like a compass or a torch.  I like Bubble Level because it's clear, no nonsense, background. It is a spirit level, no more, no less.  It is a standard level when the phone is on its side but becomes a 360¬∞ level once the phone is laid flat. This is a must for levelling the likes of washing machines or fridge freezers which need to be level to function correctly.  It even has a sound to tell you when the level is perfect so you don't need to keep your eyes glued to it.  I've used this app for a fair while and will continue to do so for as long as continues to be this good.
